title: 224: Scariest NFL players to game plan against
itunes:title: 224: Scariest NFL players to game plan against
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks list the players that keep coaches up at night game planning (15:04). The guys also break down their games of the week (1:56) and how the Steelers offense has bounced back (11:58). DJ and Bucky also re-rank the top-10 players from the 2016 draft class (20:29) before they make their college football picks (26:43).
